      "comment": "FLYING MENICE (7) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Special Envoy (23.22) in a Maiden. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expected to feature in the finish again. MISS IRENE (2) was seventh in a Maiden two back then in traffic and failed to finish last time at Healesville. Rates a leading chance on best. LADY BELMONT (3) turned in a plain performance last time when fifth at this track over 400m behind Aston Espresso (23.43) in a Bottom Up - Maiden. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. KALIAHA'S KAOS (6) should be thereabouts.",
